@page "/"

<PageTitle>RecetArre | Tu Recetario Digital</PageTitle>

<div class="cc-home">
    <div class="cc-home-hero">
        <div class="cc-home-hero-deco">🌿</div>
        <div class="container text-center py-5">
            <div class="cc-home-leaf-top">✿</div>
            <h1 class="cc-home-title">Bienvenido a RecetArre</h1>
            <p class="cc-home-sub">Tu grimorio culinario personal — guarda, comparte y descubre recetas con alma.</p>
            <div class="cc-home-actions mt-4">
                <AuthorizeView>
                    <Authorized>
                        <a href="/recetas" class="cc-btn-primary">
                            <span>📖</span> Ver mis recetas
                        </a>
                        <a href="/recetas/crear" class="cc-btn-secondary">
                            <span>✨</span> Crear receta
                        </a>
                    </Authorized>
                    <NotAuthorized>
                        <a href="/login" class="cc-btn-primary">
                            <span>🔑</span> Iniciar sesión
                        </a>
                        <a href="/registro" class="cc-btn-secondary">
                            <span>🌱</span> Crear cuenta
                        </a>
                    </NotAuthorized>
                </AuthorizeView>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                <div class="cc-feature-card">
                    <div class="cc-feature-icon">📖</div>
                    <h3 class="cc-feature-title">Tu Recetario</h3>
                    <p class="cc-feature-desc">Guarda todas tus recetas favoritas en un solo lugar, organizadas por categorías e ingredientes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                <div class="cc-feature-card">
                    <div class="cc-feature-icon">🏅</div>
                    <h3 class="cc-feature-title">Logros y Medallas</h3>
                    <p class="cc-feature-desc">Desbloquea medallas especiales mientras contribuyes con comentarios y recetas a la comunidad.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                <div class="cc-feature-card">
                    <div class="cc-feature-icon">⭐</div>
                    <h3 class="cc-feature-title">Califica y Comenta</h3>
                    <p class="cc-feature-desc">Valora las recetas de otros y deja tu opinión. Tu voz hace crecer la comunidad.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    @@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400;1,600&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&display=swap');

    :root {
        --cc-parchment: #f5f0e8;
        --cc-cream: #faf6ee;
        --cc-linen: #ede6d6;
        --cc-bark: #7a5c3a;
        --cc-moss: #5a7a4a;
        --cc-sage: #8aab7a;
        --cc-sage-pale: #c8ddb8;
        --cc-rose: #d4836a;
        --cc-ink: #3a2e22;
        --cc-muted: #8a7a68;
        --cc-border: #c8b898;
    }

    .cc-home {
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
        color: var(--cc-ink);
    }

    .cc-home-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a2f 0%, #2d5a46 60%, #354f52 100%);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 1rem 0;
    }

    .cc-home-hero-deco {
        position: absolute;
        right: 5%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
        font-size: 8rem;
        opacity: 0.07;
        pointer-events: none;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .cc-home-leaf-top {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: rgba(200, 221, 184, 0.6);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .cc-home-title {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
        color: #e8d5b0;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .cc-home-sub {
        color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.75);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        font-style: italic;
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cc-home-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .cc-btn-primary {
        background: #5a7a4a;
        color: #f5f0e8;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 30px;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
        font-family: 'Lora', serif;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(90, 122, 74, 0.35);
    }

    .cc-btn-primary:hover {
        background: #3a2e22;
        color: #f5f0e8;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .cc-btn-secondary {
        background: transparent;
        color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.85);
        border: 1.5px solid rgba(138, 171, 122, 0.5);
        border-radius: 30px;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
        font-family: 'Lora', serif;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .cc-btn-secondary:hover {
        border-color: #8aab7a;
        color: #f5f0e8;
        background: rgba(138, 171, 122, 0.1);
    }

    .cc-feature-card {
        background: #faf6ee;
        border: 1.5px solid #c8b898;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .cc-feature-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(90, 60, 30, 0.12);
    }

    .cc-feature-icon {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .cc-feature-title {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #3a2e22;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .cc-feature-desc {
        color: #8a7a68;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
    }
</style>
